item.title: Help me with my server please!
item.dc:creator: @Fate_Sealed Fate Sealed
item.description:
@Fate_Sealed wrote:

type in ur router ip. go to applications & gaming. for application, type in ur server name. for the port to port, type in ur port. for the both thing, change it to tbc, then click enable. all done.
